name: Auchenia Mandarin
description:
--Fig.16--
  Auchenia Mandarin is a creature from Awasis, an exoplanet located 320 light years from Earth, orbiting the star Nikawyi.
  Auchenia is one of the greatest predators ever seen, since it can swim, run and fly with perfection. Despite his big size, it only eats small creatures, tones of them a day.
  They are really intelligent creatures, being able to build big palace-like nests for them, with room up to 60 individuals.
